Subject: [PATCH 05/15] =?UTF-8?q?Phase=202:=20moe-split=20tool=20=E2=80=94?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20split=20MoE=20GGUF=20into=20per-node=20expert=20groups?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Splits MoE models by slicing packed expert tensors and gathering
router gate rows into per-node GGUFs. Each output contains full
trunk + assigned expert shard with updated metadata.

Supports both contiguous groups (--groups N) and custom expert
selection (--expert-list) for informed grouping.

Tested on Qwen3-30B-A3B-Q4_K_M: 17GB → 5.35GB per node (4 groups),
loads in unmodified llama.cpp, generates at 106 t/s.
